{"tid":403331,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"你地早餐食乜野","createTime":"2017-09-17T06:24:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-17T08:15:21.000Z","uid":79353,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d9b1d869d25afca5d5ff2537496285844961a748","tid":403331,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T06:24:44.000Z","msg":"A餐<br />\nWeetabix兩塊 + 生果切粒 (屋企有乜就食乜) + nuts + 水/無糖豆漿<br />\n有原味乳酪就用一杯黎點weetabix食<br />\n<br />\nB餐<br />\n滾水煮麥皮 (份量按當日食量及心情而定) +<br />\n 生果切粒 (屋企有乜就食乜) + nuts + 水/無糖豆漿<br />\n<br />\nC餐<br />\n同屋企人出去食<br />\n時菜 + 蛋通粉/米粉/米線<br />\n阿妹唔食茄汁豆俾埋我<br />\n<br />\n。。。暫時得咁多<br />\n<br />\n。。。我身體差過日日食餐蛋麵 吉豬的人。。。"},{"pid":"abb3826e77ebe935b70531f35535fe11a3b33a9d","tid":403331,"uid":93655,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T06:25:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd1665719da4ffa3784990ccd4761713dcdb909d","tid":403331,"uid":50744,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T06:26:03.000Z","msg":"邊有錢食"},{"pid":"35ee416ef3e857fcc7b8987749f2bed93de0b6fd","tid":403331,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T06:27:49.000Z","msg":"麵包、牛奶／豆漿煮麥皮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dbcd3ea702fbe6468c35a057e0f87eecddc1645","tid":403331,"uid":79353,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T06:31:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊有錢食</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/17/143029_42df940fb3a02e7a6f4fdeaa931beed9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F17%2F143029_42df940fb3a02e7a6f4fdeaa931beed9.png&h=65f4ccfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n滾水麥皮點都貴唔過魚柳炒蛋<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1cd3bd0e60a0c6c0d3d4a8dc94acc1cb34e2ea9","tid":403331,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"